---
import App from "../App.svelte";
import Layout from "../Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <header>
    <h1>üìù day notes</h1>
    <i>a simple notes app</i>
    <div>
      open source on
      <a href="https://github.com/onsclom/day-notes">github</a>
    </div>

    <div>made by <a href="https://onsclom.net">austin merrick</a></div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <p style="text-align: center">
      <i>‚ö†Ô∏è app under construction and coming soon ‚ö†Ô∏è</i>
    </p>

    <h2>about</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>‚òØÔ∏è no manual organization needed, just start writing</li>
      <li>üìñ read notes as a reverse chronological feed</li>
      <li>‚ö°Ô∏è fast, small, and works well on all devices</li>
      <li>üíæ persists notes to your browser's local storage</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>why</h2>
    <p>
      i wanted a simpler notes solution that was tailored to my personal
      workflow.
    </p>

    <h2>demo</h2>
    <div class="demo-container">
      <App client:load demo={true} />
    </div>
    <small><i>existing notes generated by chatgpt</i></small>

    <h2>plans</h2>
    <p>
      a feature i really want is cross-device sync. unfortunately, this will
      require some kind of account based auth stuff. maybe i'll just use
      something like github gists' API, or maybe i'll do something more custom.
      i'm not sure on the details yet. though i definitely want the app to be
      offline-first so it works even without an internet connection, then syncs
      if there is internet connection.
    </p>
    <p>
      besides that, i plan to dogfood the app for a bit and see what i end up
      wanting. i might make the notes markdown. i might add a search feature. i
      might add ways to export and import notes as plaintext.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem;
  }

  .demo-container {
    margin: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    height: 400px;
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1),
      0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
  }

  main {
    padding: 0.5rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  html {
    height: auto;
    font-family:
      -apple-system,
      BlinkMacSystemFont,
      avenir next,
      avenir,
      segoe ui,
      helvetica neue,
      helvetica,
      Cantarell,
      Ubuntu,
      roboto,
      noto,
      arial,
      sans-serif;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 120ch) {
    body {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: none;
    }

    header {
      padding-top: 2rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
